ENTRY            A1074   20260208   20260508   20260508       A132
SUBENT        A1074001   20260208   20260508   20260508       A132
BIB                  9         18
TITLE      Study of the 2H(d,n)3He reaction between 12 and 19 MeV
AUTHOR     (F.S.Dietrich,E.G.Adelberger,W.E.Meyerhof)
INSTITUTE  (1USASTF)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,184,449,1972)
FACILITY   (VDGT,1USASTF)
SAMPLE     A deuterium gas target. The gas pressure was one
           atmosphere, and was measured with a Bourdon gauge.
METHOD     (TOF)
REL-REF    (M,C0046001,J.E.Brolley Jr+,J,PR,107,820,1957)
           The detector efficiency was determined by using the
           2H(d,n) reaction with the cross sections determined
           by Brolley Jr, et al.
HISTORY    (19810327C) Compilation produced by Arzamas RFNC-VNIIEF
           (19990205U)CNPD: corrected 4-dig. year and lower cases.
           (20200409A) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
           MONIT-REF -> REL-REF.
           (20260208A) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           Subent 004 deleted (values from other publications).
ENDBIB              18
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           21
SUBENT        A1074002   20260208   20260508   20260508       A132
BIB                  7         18
REACTION   (1-H-2(D,N)2-HE-3,,DA)
MONITOR    (1-H-2(D,N)2-HE-3,,DA)
           The absolute scale was fixed by normalizing the average
           of the 0. degr. yields at 12 and 14 MeV to the average
           of the 0. degr. yields at 12.2 and 13.8 MeV of Brolley,
           Putnam and Rosen (see MONIT-REF).
MONIT-REF  (C0046001,J.E.Brolley Jr+,J,PR,107,820,1957)
CRITIQUE   Manfred Drosg (2020-02-20): The cross sections are
           high due to incomplete charge collection of the
           deuteron beam because of a beam-stop that was
           not thick enough.
FLAG       (1.) the data taken in the backward hemisphere,
                reflected about 90. degr.
STATUS     (CURVE,,F.S.Dietrich+,J,NP/A,184,449,1972) Fig 2
HISTORY    (20200409A) SD: SF9=EXP deleted from REACTION code.
           CRITIQUE from M.Drosg added. ANG-ERR -> ANG-ERR-D;
           DATA-ERR -> ERR-DIG. ERR-ANALYS deleted.
           (20260208U) SD: STATUS updated.
ENDBIB              18
COMMON               2          3
ANG-ERR-D  ERR-DIG
ADEG       PER-CENT
  0.5        1.
ENDCOMMON            3
